ert-amber-gun-name-patos = Patos bundle
ert-amber-gun-desc-patos = A one-handed submachinegun that punches above its weight. Keep your small magazine capacity in mind.

ert-amber-gun-name-aegun = Advanced energy gun
ert-amber-gun-desc-aegun = One advanced energy gun, for both lethal and non-lethal engagments.

ert-amber-gun-name-mixlaser = Mixed Laser bundle
ert-amber-gun-desc-mixlaser = A disabler SMG together with a Laser Carbine, bundled with a portable recharger.

ert-medkit-name = First aid kit
ert-medkit-desc = A simple first aid kit, dont get shoot too hard.

ert-brutekit-name = Brute kit
ert-brutekit-desc = A brute kit, dont get shot with lasers.

ert-drozdkit-name = Drozd bundle
ert-drozdkit-desc = A heavy submachinegun bundled with different ammo types, a NanoTrasen armaments classic.

ert-lecterkit-name = Lecter bundle
ert-lecterbundle-desc = A high-grade assault rifle packaged with a handful of magazines, precise and packs a punch, but quite bulky.

ert-IK30kit-name = IK-30 bundle
ert-IK30kit-desc = A magazine fed energy weapon packaged with a handful of magazines, for when recharging your energy gun is not an option.

ert-AutoInjectorLight-name = Auto Injectors
ert-AutoInjectorLight-desc = A handful of Autoinjectors and a roll of Gauze for bad days.

ert-AdvancedTopicals-name = Advanced Topicals
ert-AdvancedTopicals-desc = Sutures, Mesh and Bloodbags. A lot of Sutures, Mesh and Bloodbags.

ert-CombatMedkit-name = Combat Medkit
ert-CombatMedkit-desc = A combat medkit, should get you through a gunfight or two.

ert-LeaderRedOfficer-name = Officers Bundle
ert-LeaderRedOfficer-desc = A kit containing a Universal Handgun, a Advanced Laser Pistol and a trench whistle. AVANTI!

ert-LeaderRedColdCannon-name = I.C.E.E bundle
ert-LeaderRedColdCannon-desc = A I.C.E.E cannon bundled together with a portable recharger.

ert-LeaderRedWT-name = WT550 bundle
ert-LeaderRedWT-desc = The classic WT550 submachinegun, bundled together with a few magazines and two telescopic shields.

ert-enforcerkit-name = Enforcer bundle
ert-enforcerkit-desc = A Enforcer bundled with 3 boxes of buckshot.

ert-GammaOfficer-name = Officers Bundle
ert-GammaOfficer-desc = A kit containing a N1984 and a trench whistle. "Retreat? We just got here"

ert-GammaLeaderAntelope-name = Antelope bundle
ert-GammaLeaderAntelope-desc = A bundle containing a Antelope automatic shotgun and 5 drums to feed it with. Ration your ammo carefully.

ert-LeaderAtrides-name = Atreides Bundle
ert-LeaderAtrides-desc = A Atreides bundled together with two telescopic shields and 5 magazines.

ert-GammaPulseRifle-name = Pulse Rifle
ert-GammaPulseRifle-desc = A singular pulse rifle. Corporate asks you to not take this option.

ert-GammaSecCombatkit-name = Combat Medkit bundle
ert-GammaSecCombatkit-desc = A Combat Medkit bundled together with some additional auto-injectors.

ert-GammaSecStimkit-name = Stimulant bundle
ert-GammaSecStimkit-desc = A jetinjector bundled together with 2 bottles of Ephedrine and one bottle of Omnizine. Dont ask about the legality

ert-GammaSecliquidkit-name = Liquid medicine bundle
ert-GammaSecliquidkit-desc = A jetinjector bundled together with a box full of highly fragile medicine bottles.

ert-GammaWTkit-name = WT550 bundle
ert-GammaWTkit-desc = The classic WT550 bundled together with 5 magazines and 2 telescopic shields.

ert-enforcerkitspecial-name = Enforcer bundle
ert-enforcerkitspecial-desc = An Enforcer bundled together with buckshot, incendiary shells and uranium ammunition.

ert-Immolatorkit-name = Immolator bundle
ert-Immolatorkit-desc = The original firestarter bundled together with a portable recharger and an energy gun.

ert-IK60kit-name = IK-60 bundle
ert-IK60kit-desc = IK-60-M bundled together with 4 Laser magazines. Watch your ammo consumption.

ert-GammaC4-name = C4 box
ert-GammaC4-desc = 4 timed charges of plastic breaching explosives.

ert-GammaThermals-name = Special Forces gasmask
ert-GammaThermals-desc = A gasmask with both a thermal and a nightvision lense.

ert-GammaJets-name = Jetpack bundle
ert-GammaJets-desc = A jetpack bundle containing a handheld mass scanner, a better cell for it and a pair of pocket breathinggastanks.

ert-GammaNadesHE-name = Explosive grenades
ert-GammaNadesHE-desc = Three explosive grenades for the usage against soft targets.

ert-GammaSmokes-name = Smoke grenades
ert-GammaSmokes-desc = Three smoke grenades to obscure vision.

ert-GammaIncend-name = Incendiary grenades
ert-GammaIncend-desc = Two Incendiary grenades. Keep in mind your suit protects less against these.

ert-GammaEMP-name = Electro Magnetic Pulse Grenades
ert-GammaEMP-desc = A pair of EMP grenades, incase you have to disable Cyborgs or Lasers.
